<div class="content" name="PRINTER_INFO_STRESS" uuid="b026cf5c-680f-464a-8e08-675228ddd42c"><p>The <b>_PRINTER_INFO_STRESS</b> structure specifies printer
diagnostic information.<a id="Appendix_A_Target_120"></a><a aria-label="Product behavior note 120" href="e81cbc09-ab05-4a32-ae4a-8ec57b436c43#Appendix_A_120" data-linktype="relative-path">&lt;120&gt;</a> It is
a custom-<span><a href="831cd729-be7c-451e-b729-bd8d84ce4d24#gt_37e89d91-2800-49d1-9d17-45ebe167ad87" data-linktype="relative-path">marshaled</a></span> form of
the <b>_PRINTER_INFO_STRESS</b> (section <span><a href="9e94b8f4-a84b-4c96-b9ae-4b4acb3469b8" data-linktype="relative-path">2.2.1.10.1)</a></span>
