<dd>
<p><b>PrinterNameArray
(variable):</b> A string that specifies the printer name. The location of this
buffer is determined by the value of the <b>PrinterNameOffset</b> member. </p>
</dd>
<dd>
<p><b>ServerNameArray
(variable):</b> A string that specifies the server name. The location of this
buffer is determined by the value of the <b>ServerNameOffset</b> member.</p>
